Dear Governor Purdue,

As a trustee of Nash Community College, I wish to thank you for your decision to reduce the community college reversion of funds from 5% to3% under Executive Order Number 21.  This order, plus the freeing of the 1% that each college was holding in reserve, will give the colleges the means to meet the extraordinary demands being placed on the community college system.  Thank you for the trust you have placed in us, the community colleges of North Carolina, to use these funds wisely for the benefit of our great state's future.

